Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.10,0:47:35.94,DefaultSingle-J,,0,0,0,,	{\bord4}	付き合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.94,0:47:36.85,DefaultSingle-J,,0,0,0,,	{\bord4}	何の話や
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.85,0:47:37.74,DefaultSingle-J,,0,0,0,,	{\bord4}	私達は
